    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted Mazda RX-7 FD3S, featuring the high-revving 13B-REW rotary engine equipped with its signature sequential twin-turbocharger system. This example maintains excellent vacuum readings and consistent compression across all rotor faces. The front-midship engine placement and lightweight chassis provide a perfect 50/50 weight distribution, enhanced by a four-wheel double-wishbone suspension for superior kinematic response. The 5-speed manual gearbox shifts smoothly, sending power through a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, this FD remains a performance-focused icon with a robust drivetrain and crisp handling dynamics.",
